OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778000753
OL,3,CPussycat Dolls cancel US leg of world
OL,4,Ctour after poor ticket sales
OL,6,FThe Pussycat Dolls have announced they
OL,7,Fare cancelling the North American leg
OL,8,Fof their world tour, amid reports of
OL,9,Fweak ticket sales.
OL,11,FIn a statement on social media, the
OL,12,Fgroup said: "After taking an honest
OL,13,Flook at the North American run, we've
OL,14,Fmade the difficult and heartbreaking
OL,15,Fdecision to cancel all but one of the
OL,16,FNorth America dates."
OL,18,FHowever, the UK and European parts of
OL,19,Fthe tour were still moving forward "as
OL,20,Fplanned", with the band saying many
OL,21,Fshows there had already sold out.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
