FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778000753
OL,3,CPussycat Dolls cancel US leg of world
OL,4,Ctour after poor ticket sales
OL,6,FWhile the group did not directly
OL,7,Faddress ticket sales in their
OL,8,Fstatement, there had been reports that
OL,9,Fmany venues still had thousands of
OL,10,Funsold seats.
OL,12,FThey added that refunds for tickets
OL,13,Fbought through Ticketmaster and AXS,
OL,14,Fwould be "issued automatically", but
OL,15,Fthat fans who had bought tickets
OL,16,Fthrough third-party merchants would
OL,17,Fhave to "reach out to your point of
OL,18,Fpurchase".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
