FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778000753
OL,3,CPussycat Dolls cancel US leg of world
OL,4,Ctour after poor ticket sales
OL,6,FThe girl group had planned to perform
OL,7,Fa 53-date "PCD Forever" world tour
OL,8,Fstarting in June, the first 33 of
OL,9,Fwhich would have been in North America.
OL,11,FThe only show that will go ahead now
OL,12,Fis at WeHo Pride in Los Angeles on
OL,13,FJune 6.
OL,15,FThey will then begin their European
OL,16,Fleg in September, which will finish
OL,17,Fwith nine shows in the UK and Ireland
OL,18,Fin October.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
