OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778000753
OL,3,CPussycat Dolls cancel US leg of world
OL,4,Ctour after poor ticket sales
OL,6,FOn the band's Instagram page, a post
OL,7,Fsaid: "Our UK and European dates are
OL,8,Fstill moving forward as planned, and
OL,9,Fthe response has been incredible, with
OL,10,Fseveral shows already sold out.
OL,12,F"We are putting everything into making
OL,13,Fthis show a true celebration of the
OL,14,Fmusic and the memories, for the fans
OL,15,Fwho have been with us from the
OL,16,Fbeginning and those discovering us for
OL,17,Fthe first time."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
