OL,3,CPussycat Dolls cancel US leg of world
OL,4,Ctour after poor ticket sales
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FIn March, three members of the girl
OL,12,Fgroup - Nicole Scherzinger, Ashley
OL,13,FRoberts and Kimberly Wyatt - reunited
OL,14,Fas a trio to announce the tour, as
OL,15,Fwell as releasing a new single, 'Club
OL,16,FSong'.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
