PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778000753
OL,3,CPussycat Dolls cancel US leg of world
OL,4,Ctour after poor ticket sales
OL,6,FOriginally a six-piece band, former
OL,7,Fbandmates Carmit Bachar and Jessica
OL,8,FSutta claimed neither of them were
OL,9,Fasked to take part in the reunion,
OL,10,Fwith Sutta saying they both found out
OL,11,Fabout the tour publicly.
OL,13,FThe group was forced to delay a
OL,14,Fpreviously planned reunion six years
OL,15,Fago due to the Covid pandemic and a
OL,16,Flegal dispute.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
